            <thetext>Firefox 3.0.6 and below does fail to enable edit mode if the the designMode is switched at startup. 

The reason to switch the designMode was due the problem of Firefox with hiding and showing an editable iframe.  To fix this problem the designMode was switched at startup.
Unfortunately this breaks FF 3.0.6 and below.</thetext>
